| [date] | Initial: 350k per loop / 6 iterations / 2M cumulative / 6 subagents | Calibrated from production loop measurements + 30% safety buffer |

> Tune these numbers to your domain. Email-loop might need only 100k per loop. Code-review loop might need 500k. Measure 3-5 real loops, then set the cap at measured-max + 30%.
